<div class="main-container">
	<div class="about-building-text-container">From outdoor sports an cultural activites to culinary delights, Stowe has something for the entire family.  Ski <%= link_to('Mount Mansfield', 'https://www.stowe.com/')%>, Vermont's highest peak, <%= link_to('mountain bike', 'http://www.stowemountainbike.com/')%> miles of trails, hike the <%= link_to('Long Trail', 'http://longtrail.com/blog/2016/07/26/take-hike-stowe-vt')%>.  Eat at <%= link_to('Plate', 'http://www.platestowe.com/')%>, <%= link_to('The Bench', 'http://www.benchvt.com/')%>, or <%= link_to('Trattoria La Festa', 'http://www.trattoriastowe.com/')%>.  Grab a beer at <%= link_to('The Alchemist', 'https://alchemistbeer.com/')%>, <%= link_to('Idletyme Brewing Company', 'http://idletymebrewing.com/')%>, or the <%= link_to('Trapp Family Lodge', 'http://www.trappfamily.com/brewery.htm')%> <%= link_to('(Yeah, that von Trapp Family)', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4R462Ro5fqU')%>. Catch a concert presented by <%= link_to('Stowe Performing Arts', 'http://www.stoweperformingarts.com/')%>, get a little history at <%= link_to('The Vermont Ski and Snowboard Museum', 'https://www.vtssm.com/')%>, or watch glassblowing at <%= link_to('Little River Hot Glass Studio and Gallery', 'http://www.littleriverhotglass.com/')%>.  And if none of that sounds fun to you, check out even more activities, attractions, and events at <%= link_to('Go Stowe!', 'http://www.gostowe.com/thingstodo')%>.</div>
</div>